data.title: Doctor Who (2005–2022)
data.text:
The Power of the Doctor

The Thirteenth Doctor faces her final battles against Daleks, Cybermen and the Master.

Legend of the Sea Devils

The Doctor, Yaz and Dan come face to fin with some of the Doctor’s oldest adversaries.

Eve of the Daleks

On New Year’s Eve, an executioner Dalek instigates a deadly countdown to midnight.

The Vanquishers—Series 13

6/6 The forces of darkness are in control. Who is left to save the day?

Survivors of the Flux—Series 13

5/6 As the forces of evil mass, the Doctor, Yaz and Dan face impossible odds.

Village of the Angels—Series 13

4/6 In November 1967, a Devon village is haunted by the Weeping Angels.

Once, Upon Time—Series 13

3/6 On a planet that shouldn’t exist, the Doctor and her friends face a battle to survive.

War of the Sontarans—Series 13

2/6 The Doctor discovers the British army at war with Sontarans in the Crimea.

The Halloween Apocalypse—Series 13

1/6 On Halloween, all across the universe, terrifying forces are stirring. What is the Flux?
